title: 824. Next Gen Stats' Top 10 NFL Deep Passers of 2021
itunes:title: 824. Next Gen Stats' Top 10 NFL Deep Passers of 2021
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys do a deep dive on the Next Gen Stats' top 10 deep passers of 2021. Then for the rest of the show, the pair look at the rookie quarterbacks and their outlook before the 2022 season.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
